https://www.patreon.com/Tamers12345
Be there are be square... or should I say... SPARE. Join Sonic the Hedgehog and friends as they go up against their long time rival, Dr. Robotnik, in a game of bowling! Unknown to them though, that a close friend of their has left their team and joined the enemy! 

Starring:
Sonic the Hedgehog
Bartleby Montclair of Dresdin
Sonia the Hedgehog
Manic the Hedgehog
Knuckles the Echidna
Mindy Latour
Mark Latour
Uncle Chuck
Dr. Robotnick
Sleet
Dingo
